{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "scalehub-iot-api",
		"name": "ScaleHub IoT API",
		"description": "Complete API documentation for ScaleHub IoT - Weighing System Management\n\n## Base URL\n- Development: `http://localhost:8080`\n- Production: Configure your production URL\n\n## Authentication\nAll APIs (except Auth endpoints) require JWT Bearer Token.\n\n### How to use:\n1. Login via `/auth/login` to get `access_token`\n2. Set token in Authorization tab (Type: Bearer Token)\n3. Token is valid for 24 hours\n\n## Modules\n- **Authentication**: Login, refresh token, logout\n- **RBAC**: Users, Roles, Permissions management\n- **Locations**: Hierarchical location management\n- **Scales**: Scale device management with configurations\n- **Monitoring**: Real-time scale state monitoring\n- **Reports**: Export reports (Excel, Word, PDF)",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"auth": {
		"type": "bearer",
		"bearer": [
			{
				"key": "token",
				"value": "{{access_token}}",
				"type": "string"
			}
		]
	},
